INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (7,2,'2015-08-02 23:34:26','2015-08-02 23:34:26','<strong>WHO ARE Y\'ALL?</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">We are a friendly and growing community, diverse in our fitness, diverse in our running experience and diverse in our running goals and motivations. We come from all over this large neighborhood and have a lot of fun when we do! We welcome all interested folksages 18 and over.</p>\r\n<strong>HOW DO I JOIN THIS FUN and FRIENDLY GROUP?</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Fill out this 2 minute<a href=\"https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/about/join/\" target=\"_blank\">New Member Form</a>. While giving us some information to help us connect you with relevant committees and members of the <a href=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/about/\" target=\"_blank\">Council</a>, you will receive important key pieces of information about how to join in on all our activities. After filling out the form, you should get a follow-up response within 7days (but you can come and join us whenever you want!) If you have any questions, email: members@crownheightsrunningclub.nyc.</p>\r\n<strong>I\'M A ...(INSERT LEVEL HERE) - DO YOU HAVE A RUN FOR ME?</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">CHRC\'sweekly group runs (that go on ALL YEAR ROUND) are based on the type of workout, not on experience or speed. Each of our runs are open to all members, no matter where you are in your running journey.</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Our motto is: Every runnerhas something to offer. No matter what your ability or preference, don\'t be shy; come out and share with us what motivates you to run!</p>\r\n<strong>IS THERE ANY COST?</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Nope!CHRC is free to join, free to run, and free to have fun.</p>\r\n<strong>DO I HAVE TO BE A MEMBER OF NYRR TO JOIN?</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">To become a member of CHRC, we askall our members to <a href=\"https://mynyrr.nyrr.org/signup\" target=\"_blank\">register with NYRR for <strong>FREE</strong></a><strong>.</strong> You are not required to purchase membership with NYRR to participate in CHRC local runs and events. If you plan to race a lot and be an active member in the New York Running Community, purchasing a membership with NYRR is encouraged.Benefits of NYRR membership can be found <a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/join-and-give/membership\" target=\"_blank\">here.</a></p>\r\n<strong>WHERE DO YOU RUN?</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">We generally run in theCrown Heights neighborhood and Prospect Park, while our longer mileage runs can cover scenery all over Brooklyn and Manhattan! Check our <a href=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/\" target=\"_blank\">schedule </a>for opportunities to run with us!</p>\r\n<strong>WHAT ELSE DO Y\'ALL DO?</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">In addition enjoying runs and racing together, we meet up once a month in the neighborhood to catch up and meet new faces. Volunteering with <a href=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/chrc-community-girls-run/\" target=\"_blank\">Girls on the Run</a>, <a href=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/chrc-goes-camping/\" target=\"_blank\">going on outings</a> (hiking and overnight camping), eating delicious post-run food at local establishments, and having a great time are things we love and are pretty good at doing!</p>\r\n<strong>DO YOU HAVE SHIRTS?</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">We sure do! <a href=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/gear/\" target=\"_blank\">YeOlde Gear Shoppe</a> opens every few months for orders. Keep up to date on our <a href=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/news/\" target=\"_blank\">News </a>Page about when orders are being taken.Our logo and shirts are member-designed and locally produced by <a href=\"http://goodtoyprintlab.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Good Toy Print Lab</a>. Checkit out!</p>\r\n<strong>WHAT\'S #RUNNINGROYALTY?</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">#RunningRoyalty is our slogan - tag us up on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CrownHeightsRC\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter </a>and <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/crownheightsrunningclub/\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a>!</p>\r\n<strong>WHAT\'S #CHRCNegativeSplit?</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">#CHRCNegativeSplit refers to our team members that choose to run races in Banana Costume. We are easily identifiable at races both on and off the course. If you see a #CHRCNegativeSplit, be sure to say hello!</p>','FAQs','','publish','open','open','','faqs','','','2017-04-27 22:45:44','2017-04-27 22:45:44','',0,'http://crownheights.dev/?page_id=6',0,'page','',0),(8,2,'2015-08-02 23:38:23','2015-08-02 23:38:23','Crown Heights Running Club embraces the diversity of our members and the breadth of our neighborhood. We wantto bring neighbors and runners together ina fun, safe, and inclusive community while supporting each member reach their goals through group runs, social events, and volunteering.\r\n\r\nOur group is made up of all paces and experience levels - we believe that every runner has something to offer. Our vision is for members to meet friends and running buddies; train together; to share ourstrengths and resources. Let\'sexplore all that Crown Heights has to offer!To become a member of the #RunningRoyalty, <a href=\"mailto:runningroyalty01@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">contact us </a>today!\r\n<h2 class=\"h1\">The Royal Council</h2>','About','','publish','open','open','','about','','','2017-04-27 23:37:51','2017-04-27 23:37:51','',0,'http://crownheights.dev/?page_id=8',0,'page','',0),(11,2,'2015-08-02 23:39:46','2015-08-02 23:39:46','<h3>Free and Fun<i>!</i>\nOpen to all levels\nJoining is simple as showing up</h3>\n<h1>EVENTS SCHEDULE</h1>\n[gcal id=\"117\"]\n\n[mc4wp_form id=\"513\"]','Schedule','','publish','open','open','','schedule','','','2015-08-02 23:39:46','2015-08-02 23:39:46','',0,'http://crownheights.dev/?page_id=11',0,'page','',0),(15,2,'2015-08-02 23:43:22','2015-08-02 23:43:22','Far far away, behind the word mountains, far from the countries Vokalia and Consonantia, there live the blind texts. Separated they live in Bookmarksgrove right at the coast of the Semantics, a large language ocean. A small river named Duden flows by their place and supplies it with the necessary regelialia.\n\nIt is a paradisematic country, in which roasted parts of sentences fly into your mouth. Even the all-powerful Pointing has no control about the blind texts it is an almost unorthographic life One day however a small line of blind text by the name of Lorem Ipsum decided to leave for the far World of Grammar.\n\nThe Big Oxmox advised her not to do so, because there were thousands of bad Commas, wild Question Marks and devious Semikoli, but the Little Blind Text didnt listen. She packed her seven versalia, put her initial into the belt and made herself on the way. When she reached the first hills of the Italic Mountains, she had a last view back on the skyline of her hometown Bookmarksgrove, the headline of Alphabet Village and the subline of her own road, the Line Lane. Pityful a rethoric question ran over her cheek, then\n\n[gallery gallery_type=\"grid\" gallery_captions=\"true\" gallery_image_size=\"medium\" ids=\"161,163,151\"]','New #CHRC Web Site!','','publish','open','open','','its-a-new-web-site','','','2015-08-02 23:43:22','2015-08-02 23:43:22','',0,'http://crownheights.dev/?p=15',0,'post','',0),(17,2,'2015-08-02 23:43:44','2015-08-02 23:43:44','','News','','publish','open','closed','','news','','','2015-08-02 23:43:44','2015-08-02 23:43:44','',0,'http://crownheights.dev/?page_id=17',0,'page','',0),(24,2,'2015-08-05 22:46:15','2015-08-05 22:46:15','','10959837_828536543850892_8392615958687216162_n','','inherit','open','open','','10959837_828536543850892_8392615958687216162_n','','','2015-08-05 22:46:15','2015-08-05 22:46:15','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2015/08/10959837_8285365438