-17 15:00:32','2017-04-17 15:00:32','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/?p=561',0,'post','',0),(577,3,'2016-03-29 17:54:33','2016-03-29 17:54:33','On Sunday, March 6, more than 5000 runners participated in one of NYRR\'s favorites, the <a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2016/nyrr-washington-heights-salsa-blues-and-shamrocks-5k\" target=\"_blank\">Salsa, Blues and Shamrock 5K</a> in Washington Heights!\n\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-580\" src=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2016/03/IMG_2501-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"Racing\" width=\"296\" height=\"245\" />\n\nAmong them were the lucky 13 #CHRCMen and #CHRCWomen accompanied by one special Leprechaun cheering on the sidelines at the finish. Members of theteam had been preparing for this hilly race through the month of Februaryand others used this as a training race for their bigger events of the 2016 spring racing season.\n\nWith five male finishers, this was a debut finish for the #CHRCMen\'s team - meaning that the team had enough people to pool their results and get scored for club points! Congratulations to our men\'s team!!\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style=\"text-align: justify\">This is #CHRCWomen\'s second year in the Club Standings and it\'s certainly a strong start! The ladies ran with smiles for miles to bring in fourpoints and a 6th place standing for Open Women B (20th overall). Now that\'s a smashing start to the 2016 season!!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-578\" src=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2016/03/IMG_2465-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"Post-race Breakfast\" width=\"424\" height=\"318\" /><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581\" src=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2016/03/IMG_2502-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"CHRC\" width=\"318\" height=\"318\" /></p>\nBig thanksto our Lucky Leprechaun (aka Akil) who cheered our 200m finish! We celebrated with a Dominican breakfast at Malecon. It was a CHRC kind ofmorning.\n<h2><strong>NEXT UP...</strong></h2>\nOur second Club Points race is this Saturday April 2nd at the <a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2016/scotland-run-10k\" target=\"_blank\">Scotland 10K</a> in Central Park! Both #CHRCWomen and #CHRCMen have full teams toeing the start line.Bring a sprig of heather and blare the bagpipes! These runners are ready for some fun!Here\'s tae ye!Here\'s tae us!\n\nJoin us afterward for some tattie scones and a <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1575312129447262/\" target=\"_blank\">party to celebrate</a> at <a href=\"http://www.bergn.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Berg\'n </a>in Crown Heights! All are welcome.\n\n&nbsp;','Ready, Set... Go #CHRC!','','publish','closed','closed','','ready-set-go-chrc','','','2017-04-17 15:00:32','2017-04-17 15:00:32','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/?p=577',0,'post','',0),(578,2,'2016-03-29 17:17:42','2016-03-29 17:17:42','','Post-race Breakfast','','inherit','closed','closed','','img_2465','','','2016-03-29 17:17:42','2016-03-29 17:17:42','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/03/IMG_2465.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(579,2,'2016-03-29 17:40:25','2016-03-29 17:40:25','','Washington Heights 5k 2016','','inherit','closed','closed','','washington-heights-5k-2016','','','2016-03-29 17:40:25','2016-03-29 17:40:25','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/03/Washington-Heights-5k-2016-e1459273254928.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(580,2,'2016-03-29 17:42:32','2016-03-29 17:42:32','','Racing','','inherit','closed','closed','','img_2501','','','2016-03-29 17:42:32','2016-03-29 17:42:32','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/03/IMG_2501.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(581,2,'2016-03-29 17:42:41','2016-03-29 17:42:41','','CHRC','','inherit','closed','closed','','img_2502','','','2016-03-29 17:42:41','2016-03-29 17:42:41','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/03/IMG_2502.jpg',