k\" target=\"_blank\">Queens 10k</a>, and the <a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2016/front-runners-new-york-lgbt-pride-run-5m\" target=\"_blank\">Pride Run 5M</a>! Both are sold out but the<a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2016/nyrr-team-championships-women-5m\" target=\"_blank\">Team Champions 5M (Women)</a> and <a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2016/nyrr-team-championships-men-5m\" target=\"_blank\">Team Champions 5M (Men)</a> is still available; sign up and rep CHRC in this exclusive team only event!','Race Report: Retro Run 4M and New York Mini 10k','','publish','closed','closed','','race-report-retro-run-4m-mini-10k','','','2017-04-17 15:06:13','2017-04-17 15:06:13','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/?p=781',0,'post','',0),(784,2,'2016-06-16 03:02:49','2016-06-16 03:02:49','','retro run 2016','','inherit','closed','closed','','retro-run-2016','','','2016-06-16 03:02:49','2016-06-16 03:02:49','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/06/retro-run-2016.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(787,3,'2016-06-19 04:47:32','2016-06-19 04:47:32','<p style=\"text-align: left\">On June 12, the Crown Heights Running Royalty took their first group adventure to <a href=\"http://nysparks.com/parks/13/details.aspx\">Bear Mountain State Park</a>. Led by Duchess Kaitlyn, this band of gentry soughta day in the lapof Nature while straying not too far from their noble lands.</p>\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-789\" src=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2016/06/bearmtn2-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"bearmtn2\" width=\"362\" height=\"204\" /><img class=\"wp-image-794 alignleft\" src=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2016/06/bearmtn7-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"bearmtn7\" width=\"362\" height=\"204\" />\n\n<span style=\"line-height: 1.42857\">From Brooklyn, some traveled by car and others by direct bus. They all met in the State Park with the intent to conquer new Heights, appreciate the arrival of warm weather, and take in a view of NYC from a distance. At the end of the day, the Royal Crew agreed that they had attained all that they set out to do; and it only required a short day trip, a packed lunch, some sturdy shoes and a bit of cash for post-hike beers and ice cream!</span>\n\n<span style=\"line-height: 1.42857\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-792\" src=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2016/06/bearmtn5-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"bearmtn5\" width=\"363\" height=\"204\" /><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-797\" src=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2016/06/bearmtn10-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"bearmtn10\" width=\"363\" height=\"204\" /></span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-790\" src=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2016/06/bearmtn3-e1466310975688.jpg\" alt=\"bearmtn3\" width=\"200\" height=\"270\" />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\nKaitlyn promises to lead more adventure hikes by the season; however, you wont have to wait long before the next great adventure! Next month, on the weekend of July 16-17, Sunny, our Social Media Baron and Grand Keeper of Records, Louie will be taking CHRC out on an overnight camping trip! This time, there may even be a bit of trail running involved (^o^)\n\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1409241642434584/\">Sign up on the Royal Bulletin</a> before they take off without you. No experience required. Pleasecontact runningroyalty@gmail.com or talk to Sunnyas soon as possible to ensure the best experience!\n\n&nbsp;\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center\"></h5>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center\"></h5>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #008000\"><strong>CHRCOUTDOORSCHRCOUTDOORSCHRCOUTDOORSCHRCOUTDOORSCHRCOUTDOORSCHRCOUTDOORSCHRCOUTDOORS</strong></span></h5>\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-791\" src=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2016/06/bearmtn4-300x238.jpg\" alt=\"bearmtn4\" width=\"400\" height=\"317\" />\n\n&nbsp;','CHRC Outdoors: The First Adventure','','publish','closed','closed','','chrc-outdoors-adventure-fresh-air','','','2017-04-17 15:00:32','2017-04-17 15:00:32','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/?p=787',0,'post','',0),(788,2,'2016-06-19 04:06:04','2016-06-19 04:06:04','','bearmtn1','','inherit','closed','closed','','bearmtn1','','','2016-06-19 04:06:04','2016-06-19 04:06:04','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/06/bearmtn1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(789,2,'2016-06-19 04:06:05','2016-06-19 04:06:05','','bearmtn2','','inherit','closed','closed','','bearmtn2','','','2016-06-19 04:06:05','2016-06-19 04:06:05','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/06/bearmtn2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(790,2,'2016-06-19 04:06:06','2016-06-19 04:06:06','','bearmtn3','','inherit','closed','closed','','bearmtn3','','','2016-06-19 04:06:06','2016-06-19 04:06:06','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/06/bearmtn3-e1466310975688.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(791,2,'2016-06-19 04:06:07','2016-06-19 04:06:07','','bearmtn4','','inherit','closed','closed','','bearmtn4','','','2016-06-19 04:06:07','2016-06-19 04:06:07','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/06/bearmtn4.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(792,2,'2016-06-19 04:06:08','2016-06-19 04:06:08','','bearmtn5','','inherit','closed','closed','','bearmtn5','','','2016-06-19 04:06:08','2016-06-19 04:06:08','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/06/bearmtn5.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(793,2,'2016-06-19 04:06:09','2016-06-19 04:06:09','','bearmtn6','','inherit','closed','closed','','bearmtn6','','','2016-06-19 04:06:09','2016-06-19 04:06:09','',0,'http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/06/bearmtn6.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(794,2,'2016-06-19 04:06:10','2016-06-19 04:06:10','','bearmtn7','','