 contact@crownheightsrunningclub.nyc\r\n\r\nAnd don\'t miss the excitement of the <a href=\"http://www.baa.org/\">121st running of the Boston Marathon </a>on April 17th! There will be live coverage online, and Boston is a short bus/train ride away for an up close look.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<strong>MEET YOUR ROYAL COUNCIL!</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1250 alignleft\" src=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2017/03/IMG_4213-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"377\" height=\"282\" />CHRC is 100% organized and run on member involvement!\r\n\r\nBrowse our <a href=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/about/\">bio page</a> to get to know a little about the fuel that runs this Club, and consider joining us! All members are welcome.\r\n\r\nWe rely on our running family to ensure that ourcommunity continues to grow and meet the needs of its fabulous royalty. If you are interested in contributing your skills, enthusiasm and a little time, join one of our <a href=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/about/\">three committees</a> (Community, Events, Run Leaders) or consider joining the <a href=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/about/\">Royal Council.</a>\r\n\r\nEmail us &lt;contact@crownheightsrunningclub.nyc&gt; and let us know how you would like to get involved!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','This Week\'s Announcements','','inherit','closed','closed','','1246-revision-v1','','','2017-04-14 04:30:41','2017-04-14 04:30:41','',1246,'https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/1246-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1319,2,'2017-04-14 04:31:36','2017-04-14 04:31:36','<h3>Week ofApril 3 -April 9</h3>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"js_34s\" class=\"_5pbx userContent\">\r\n<div id=\"id_58e411736fefe4b55058828\" class=\"text_exposed_root text_exposed\">\r\n\r\n<strong>SPRING GROUP RUN SCHEDULE<img class=\" wp-image-1251 alignright\" src=\"http://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2017/03/IMG_2714-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"349\" height=\"262\" /></strong>\r\n\r\nIt\'a Spring, w