am gear and also support our club.\r\n\r\nNot racing? No problem. We\'ve got some sweet neon cotton blended gear &amp; headbands for you to wear out to the cheer squads!\r\n\r\nYou can purchase<a href=\"https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/merch/\">all CHRC gear DIRECT from our website!!</a>\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1559 alignleft\" src=\"https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2017/04/chrc_new_id_01-274x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"299\" height=\"327\" /><img class=\"wp-image-1561 alignleft\" src=\"https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2017/04/chrc_new_id_03-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"219\" height=\"329\" />Look for *NEW VINTAGE* and *LIMITED EDITION : BROOKLYN HALF 2017*\r\n\r\nLet\'s show off our crowns and banners at the Brooklyn Half!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAll gear will be distributed one week prior to the <a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2017/airbnb-brooklyn-half\">Brooklyn Half.</a> A secondary pick-up time will be provided for distribution at the <a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2017/airbnb-brooklyn-half/pre-party-presented-by-new-balance\">Brooklyn Half Pre-Party</a>.\r\n\r\n*Sample sizes for try-ons will be available at the April Meet\'nGreet\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>#CHRCTRAIL -BLAZERS WELCOME SPRING, CELEBRATE EARTH DAY</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1576 \" src=\"https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2017/04/IMG_4698-e1493051589731-300x221.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"291\" height=\"215\" />Although #CHRCTrails and a high interest in hiking and camping has been a unique feature of our club since the beginning, we are seeing an increase of participation in and trail/ultra racing this year.\r\n\r\nIn the past couple of weekends, #CHRCTrails have climbed peaks and waded through creeks as they ran miles in the gorgeous landscapes of upstate New York. A more thorough account is forthcoming from our enthusiastic Sunday Trails Run Leader, Joey, so stay tuned!\r\n\r\nFor members interested in off-roading, come out for <a href=\"https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/\">Prospect Park Trail runs on Sundays at 11am</a>. We\'re also looking forward to organizing another camping or day-hike trip this summer for those interested in havinga more casual time in nature.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<strong>RACE SIGN-UPS</strong>\r\n\r\nNYRR Summer and Fall race registrations have opened for NYRR Members TODAY and will be open to the public very soon after. These include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2017/tcs-new-york-city-marathon-long-training-run-1\">TCS NYC Marathon Long Training Run #1</a>on July 22, 2017</li>\r\n 	<li>**CLUB POINTS RACE** <a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2017/nyrr-team-championships-men-5m\">Team Champs! </a>on August 5, 2017</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2017/tcs-new-york-city-marathon-long-training-run-2\">TCS NYC Marathon Long Training Run #2 </a>on August 13, 2017</li>\r\n 	<li>**CLUB POINTS RACE** <a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2017/percy-sutton-harlem-5k-run\">Percy Sutton Harlem 5K</a> on August 26, 2017</li>\r\n 	<li>**CLUB POINTS RACE** <a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2017/new-balance-5th-avenue-mile\">New Balance 5th Avenue Mile</a> on September 10, 2017</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2017/tcs-new-york-city-marathon-tune-up-18m\">TCS NYC Marathon Tune-Up (18miles)</a> on September 17, 2017</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_163\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"300\"]<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-163\" src=\"https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2015/09/11695828_10152994258207401_3941038848530298842_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> Team Champs[/caption]\r\n\r\nThere is still space for registration in the <a href=\"http://www.nyrr.org/races-and-events/2017/new-balance-bronx-10-mile\">Bronx 10Mile </a>and <a href