ag Check:</span></b></div>\r\n<div>Wave 1: Eastern Parkway at Bedford Ave -- <i><b>CLOSES AT <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1274764871\"><span class=\"aQJ\">6:10 AM</span></span></b></i></div>\r\n<div>Wave 2: Grand Army Plaza at Eastern Parkway -- <i><b>CLOSES AT <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1274764872\"><span class=\"aQJ\">7:00 AM</span></span></b></i></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Pacing: </span></b>Why run alone? Record your goals and collaborate <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1VOW0NYMMCQahkd1veY3aUyI2BngqKZJMD3jeFXfHKlQ/edit#gid=0\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1VOW0NYMMCQahkd1veY3aUyI2BngqKZJMD3jeFXfHKlQ/edit%23gid%3D0&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1494611427760000&amp;usg=AFQjCNG2G4R_8wD_hII55uqWQGyxg6luMw\">with Team CHRC with this wonderful spreadsheet!</a></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Photo,</span></b><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Restrooms,</span></b><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Warm Up</span></b><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">:</span></b><u>Please meet us at <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1274764873\"><span class=\"aQJ\">6:20AM</span></span> by the Botanical Gardens for a team photo,</u> and then a warm up job! Restrooms are available beside the Botanical Gardens, and on Eastern Parkway just east of Underhill Ave.</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFor those of you NOT racing but want to participate in this all Brooklyn event and cheer on your teammates or clubmates, we will have a CHEER STATION!\r\n\r\nWell be stationed on the southwest corner of Ocean parkway and Avenue U with the CHRC banner and signs. The race starts at 7am so well start seeing runners a little after 8am. Racers, don\'t forget to look for us for your personalized high-five and CHRC boost!\r\n\r\nDave will be there at 7:30 am to get everything set up. Please feel free to bring snacks &amp; drinks for the cheerers (donuts, coffee, margaritasetc) and the runners (bananas, oranges, gu..). We\'ll pack up around 11:00am and join the Post Race Celebration at L&amp;B Spumoni Gardens!\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><u><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: large;\">POST-RACE CELEBRATION</span></u></div>\r\n<div>Look for #<span class=\"m_2603364830087274922gmail-il\">CHRC</span>at baggage claim in MCU Park! Please check in with me, even if just to say you finished.<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><b>Gideon (Check your email for his cell number)</b>,</span>but we hope to see you! ***Note: Cellular service is usuallyspotty at the park and finish!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><b>***Breakfast/Food/Celebration*<wbr />**: </b>Join us after the race for a slice of Sicilian at<a href=\"http://www.spumonigardens.com/dining-room\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.spumonigardens.com/dining-room&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1494611427760000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFYVRL3y4kl0F-t5M3ANz5IsOCtQg\">Spumoni\'s!</a>After you pick up your bag at MCU Park (home of the Brooklyn Cyclones), walk over to the D train at Coney Island/Stillwell Ave, ride 2 stops to 25 Ave, and walk on in!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to contactGideon.</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','AirBnB Brooklyn Half: All you need (plus your amazing legs)','','inherit','closed','closed','','1632-revision-v1','','','2017-05-11 17:57:38','2017-05-11 17:57:38','',1632,'https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/1632-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1635,3,'2017-05-11 20:38:52','2017-05-11 20:38:52','','IMG_2752','','inherit','open','closed','','img_2752','','','2017-05-11 20:38:52','2017-05-11 20:38:52','',1632,'https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2017/05/IMG_2752.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1636,3,'2017-05-11 20:43:57','2017-05-11 