G_1062-e1464982782177-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a></u></span></div>\r\n<div><b></b></div>\r\n<div><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Bag Check:</span></b></div>\r\n<div>Wave 1: Eastern Parkway at Bedford Ave -- <i><b>CLOSES AT <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1274764871\"><span class=\"aQJ\">6:10 AM</span></span></b></i></div>\r\n<div>Wave 2: Grand Army Plaza at Eastern Parkway -- <i><b>CLOSES AT <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1274764872\"><span class=\"aQJ\">7:00 AM</span></span></b></i></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Pacing: </span></b>Why run alone? Record your goals and collaborate <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1VOW0NYMMCQahkd1veY3aUyI2BngqKZJMD3jeFXfHKlQ/edit#gid=0\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1VOW0NYMMCQahkd1veY3aUyI2BngqKZJMD3jeFXfHKlQ/edit%23gid%3D0&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1494611427760000&amp;usg=AFQjCNG2G4R_8wD_hII55uqWQGyxg6luMw\">with Team CHRC with this wonderful spreadsheet!</a></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Photo,</span></b><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Restrooms,</span></b><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Warm Up</span></b><b><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">:</span></b><u>Please meet us at <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1274764873\"><span class=\"aQJ\">6:20AM</span></span> by the Botanical Gardens for a team photo,</u> and then a warm up job! Restrooms are available beside the Botanical Gardens, and on Eastern Parkway just east of Underhill Ave.</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<strong>#CHRC CHEER STATION @7:30AM</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1095 alignleft\" src=\"https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/12/cheertable-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"333\" height=\"250\" />For those of you NOT racing but want to participate in this all Brooklyn event and cheer on your teammates or clubmates, we will have a CHEER STATION!\r\n\r\nWell be stationed on the southwest corner of <strong>Ocean parkway and Avenue U</strong> with the CHRC banner and signs. Weexpect to start seeing runners a little after 8am. Racers, with about 5K to go, don\'t forget to look for us for your personalized high-five and super #CHRC boost!\r\n\r\nPlease feel free to bring snacks &amp; drinks for the cheerers (donuts, coffee, margaritasetc) and the runners (bananas, oranges, gu..). We\'ll pack up around 11:00am and join the Post Race Celebration at <a href=\"http://www.spumonigardens.com/dining-room\">L&amp;B Spumoni Gardens</a>!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div><u><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: large;\">POST-RACE CELEBRATION<img class=\" wp-image-762 alignright\" src=\"https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/06/IMG_2755-e1464982588183-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"351\" height=\"351\" /></span></u></div>\r\n<div>HUZZAH!! YOU DID IT! Let us help you enjoy the rest of your day and your recovery! Look for #<span class=\"m_2603364830087274922gmail-il\">CHRC</span>at baggage claim in MCU Park! Please check in with <strong>Gideon (check your email for his cell number)</strong>, even if just to say you finished,but we hope to see you at baggage claim or Breakfast! ***Note: Cellular service is usuallyspotty at the park and finish!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><b>***Breakfast/Food/Celebration*<wbr />**: </b>The Finish area is quite a zoo and it may be hard to find each other. Once you\'ve stretched out, gotten your things and enjoyed a beer in the park,Join us a little bit away for a slice of Sicilian at<a href=\"http://www.spumonigardens.com/dining-room\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.spumonigardens.com/dining-room&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1494611427760000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFYVRL3y4kl0F-t5M3ANz5IsOCtQg\">Spumoni\'s!</a>Walk yourself over (you can do it!) to the D train at Coney