s and collaborate <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1VOW0NYMMCQahkd1veY3aUyI2BngqKZJMD3jeFXfHKlQ/edit#gid=0\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1VOW0NYMMCQahkd1veY3aUyI2BngqKZJMD3jeFXfHKlQ/edit%23gid%3D0&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1494611427760000&amp;usg=AFQjCNG2G4R_8wD_hII55uqWQGyxg6luMw\">with Team CHRC with this wonderful spreadsheet!</a></div>\r\n<div><strong></strong></div>\r\n<div><strong>Photo,Restrooms,Warm Up:</strong>Please meet us at 6:20AM by the Botanical Gardens for a team photo, and then a warm up job! Restrooms are available beside the Botanical Gardens, and on Eastern Parkway just east of Underhill Ave.</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<strong>#CHRC CHEER STATION @7:30AM</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1095 alignleft\" src=\"https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/12/cheertable-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"316\" height=\"237\" />For those of you NOT racing but want to participate in this all Brooklyn event and cheer on your teammates or clubmates, we will have a CHEER STATION!\r\n\r\nWell be stationed on the southwest corner of <strong>Ocean parkway and Avenue U</strong> with the CHRC banner and signs. Weexpect to start seeing runners a little after 8am. Racers, with about 5K to go, don\'t forget to look for us for your personalized high-five and super #CHRC boost!\r\n\r\nPlease feel free to bring snacks &amp; drinks for the cheerers (donuts, coffee, margaritasetc) and the runners (bananas, oranges, gu..). We\'ll pack up around 11:00am and join the Post Race Celebration at <a href=\"http://www.spumonigardens.com/dining-room\">L&amp;B Spumoni Gardens</a>!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div><u><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: large;\">POST-RACE CELEBRATION</span></u></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img class=\"alignright\" src=\"https://crownheightsrunningclub.nyc/app/uploads/2016/06/IMG_2755-e1464982588183-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"